title: Michael Moores Where to Invade Next Gets Release Date
text:
Michael Moore's 'Where to Invade Next' Gets Release Date 
Hollywood Reporter Saturday 24th October, 2015 
will hit theaters in Los Angeles and New York on Dec. 23 for an Oscar-qualifying run. The doc will receive a nationwide opening on Jan. 15. 
The announcement, made by the new unnamed company that will release the film, confirms what...
